{"thag16.6:0.1":"Theragatha 16.6 ","thag16.6:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.6:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.6:0.4":"Selattheragatha ","thag16.6:1.1":"“Paripunnakayo suruci, ","thag16.6:1.2":"Sujato carudassano; ","thag16.6:1.3":"Suvannavannosi bhagava, ","thag16.6:1.4":"Susukkadathosi viriyava. ","thag16.6:2.1":"Narassa hi sujatassa, ","thag16.6:2.2":"ye bhavanti viyanjana; ","thag16.6:2.3":"Sabbe te tava kayasmim, ","thag16.6:2.4":"mahapurisalakkhana. ","thag16.6:3.1":"Pasannanetto sumukho, ","thag16.6:3.2":"braha uju patapava; ","thag16.6:3.3":"Majjhe samanasanghassa, ","thag16.6:3.4":"adiccova virocasi. ","thag16.6:4.1":"Kalyanadassano bhikkhu, ","thag16.6:4.2":"kancanasannibhattaco; ","thag16.6:4.3":"Kim te samanabhavena, ","thag16.6:4.4":"evam uttamavannino. ","thag16.6:5.1":"Raja arahasi bhavitum, ","thag16.6:5.2":"cakkavatti rathesabho; ","thag16.6:5.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","thag16.6:5.4":"jambusandassa issaro. ","thag16.6:6.1":"Khattiya bhogi rajano, ","thag16.6:6.2":"anuyanta bhavanti te; ","thag16.6:6.3":"Rajabhiraja manujindo, ","thag16.6:6.4":"rajjam karehi gotama”. ","thag16.6:7.1":"“Rajahamasmi sela, ","thag16.6:7.2":"(selati bhagava) ","thag16.6:7.3":"Dhammaraja anuttaro; ","thag16.6:7.4":"Dhammena cakkam vattemi, ","thag16.6:7.5":"Cakkam appativattiyam”. ","thag16.6:8.1":"“Sambuddho patijanasi, ","thag16.6:8.2":"(iti selo brahmano) ","thag16.6:8.3":"Dhammaraja anuttaro; ","thag16.6:8.4":"‘Dhammena cakkam vattemi’, ","thag16.6:8.5":"Iti bhasatha gotama. ","thag16.6:9.1":"Ko nu senapati bhoto, ","thag16.6:9.2":"savako satthuranvayo; ","thag16.6:9.3":"Ko tetamanuvatteti, ","thag16.6:9.4":"dhammacakkam pavattitam”. ","thag16.6:10.1":"“Maya pavattitam cakkam, ","thag16.6:10.2":"(selati bhagava) ","thag16.6:10.3":"Dhammacakkam anuttaram; ","thag16.6:10.4":"Sariputto anuvatteti, ","thag16.6:10.5":"Anujato tathagatam. ","thag16.6:11.1":"Abhinneyyam abhinnatam, ","thag16.6:11.2":"bhavetabbanca bhavitam; ","thag16.6:11.3":"Pahatabbam pahinam me, ","thag16.6:11.4":"tasma buddhosmi brahmana. ","thag16.6:12.1":"Vinayassu mayi kankham, ","thag16.6:12.2":"adhimuccassu brahmana; ","thag16.6:12.3":"Dullabham dassanam hoti, ","thag16.6:12.4":"sambuddhanam abhinhaso. ","thag16.6:13.1":"Yesam ve dullabho loke, ","thag16.6:13.2":"patubhavo abhinhaso; ","thag16.6:13.3":"Soham brahmana buddhosmi, ","thag16.6:13.4":"sallakatto anuttaro. ","thag16.6:14.1":"Brahmabhuto atitulo, ","thag16.6:14.2":"marasenappamaddano; ","thag16.6:14.3":"Sabbamitte vase katva, ","thag16.6:14.4":"modami akutobhayo”. ","thag16.6:15.1":"“Idam bhonto nisametha, ","thag16.6:15.2":"yatha bhasati cakkhuma; ","thag16.6:15.3":"Sallakatto mahaviro, ","thag16.6:15.4":"sihova nadati vane. ","thag16.6:16.1":"Brahmabhutam atitulam, ","thag16.6:16.2":"marasenappamaddanam; ","thag16.6:16.3":"Ko disva nappasideyya, ","thag16.6:16.4":"api kanhabhijatiko. ","thag16.6:17.1":"Yo mam icchati anvetu, ","thag16.6:17.2":"yo va nicchati gacchatu; ","thag16.6:17.3":"Idhaham pabbajissami, ","thag16.6:17.4":"varapannassa santike”. ","thag16.6:18.1":"“Etance ruccati bhoto, ","thag16.6:18.2":"sammasambuddhasasanam; ","thag16.6:18.3":"Mayampi pabbajissama, ","thag16.6:18.4":"varapannassa santike”. ","thag16.6:19.1":"“Brahmana tisata ime, ","thag16.6:19.2":"yacanti panjalikata; ","thag16.6:19.3":"‘Brahmacariyam carissama, ","thag16.6:19.4":"bhagava tava santike’”. ","thag16.6:20.1":"“Svakkhatam brahmacariyam, ","thag16.6:20.2":"(selati bhagava) ","thag16.6:20.3":"Sanditthikamakalikam; ","thag16.6:20.4":"Yattha amogha pabbajja, ","thag16.6:20.5":"Appamattassa sikkhato”. ","thag16.6:21.1":"“Yam tam saranamagamha, ","thag16.6:21.2":"ito atthame cakkhuma; ","thag16.6:21.3":"Sattarattena bhagava, ","thag16.6:21.4":"dantamha tava sasane. ","thag16.6:22.1":"Tuvam buddho tuvam sattha, ","thag16.6:22.2":"tuvam marabhibhu muni; ","thag16.6:22.3":"Tuvam anusaye chetva, ","thag16.6:22.4":"tinno taresimam pajam. ","thag16.6:23.1":"Upadhi te samatikkanta, ","thag16.6:23.2":"asava te padalita; ","thag16.6:23.3":"Sihova anupadano, ","thag16.6:23.4":"pahinabhayabheravo. ","thag16.6:24.1":"Bhikkhavo tisata ime, ","thag16.6:24.2":"titthanti panjalikata; ","thag16.6:24.3":"Pade vira pasarehi, ","thag16.6:24.4":"naga vandantu satthuno”ti. ","thag16.6:24.5":"… Selo thero …. "}